ąIn Loving Memory of JEAN KATHLEEN LEIGHTON DAVIES
30 NOV 1920 - 17 NOV 1982
Wife of JOHN, Mother of JAMES & HELEN & Grandmother
AND THOU
BESIDE ME SINGING IN THE WILDERNESS
AND WILDERNESS IS PARADISE NOW"ķ
µIn memory of
TONY & SHEILA MOORE
06.09.33 - 18.02.94
21.04.34 - 18.08.99
from Julie. Woody. Fenton & Bailey-Rose: your daughter and her family
that you never got to meet, May they come to know you as we all sit here together."¶
